---
/* About section — two-column brutalist grid with CV download */
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-label">
    <span class="label-text">About</span>
    <a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cv-link">
      CV ↓
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="about-content">
    <h2 class="reveal">Code. Math. Finance. Always learning.</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
      I hold an Associate Degree in Software Development from Spain, using it as foundation I have teached myself many
			concepts beyond that, like AI/ML, systems programming and the basis of real time and live trading systems.
    </p>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
      I am drawn to complex problems and to many other areas of knowledge, specially economics, math, finance and Spanish history.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 0;
    border-top: var(--border);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-left: var(--border);
    border-right: var(--border);
  }

  /* ── Label column ── */
  .about-label {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    color: var(--fg);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-right: var(--border);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .about-label::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 40px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .cv-link {
    color: var(--fg);
    text-decoration: none;
		border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .cv-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ── Content column ── */
  .about-content {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    max-width: 22ch;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .about-content h2::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
    opacity: 0.75;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      border-left: none;
      border-right: none;
    }

    .about-label {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: var(--border);
      position: static;
      height: auto;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-label::after {
      display: none;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 7vw, 3rem);
    }
  }
</style>
